705438f-a.title: Brooklyn: Liberty Avenue - Hendrix Street
705438f-a.text:
546 Liberty Ave., south side, east of Hendrix Street, sho ing the home
of the first East New York Police Station. It was rented in 1871 and
occupied until 1873.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
